Package jetbrains.mps.persistence

Interface DataLocationAwareModelFactory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelFactory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryModelFactory, DefaultModelPersistence, FilePerRootModelFactory
    public interface DataLocationAwareModelFactory
extends ModelFactory
    DataSource is a plain data location, and should not know about snode, smodel, et cetera. This ~mixin interface contains knowledge about the model data location. It expresses this locations via DataSource
    Since:
    16/07/2020
